message:
feat(ws): integrate WebSocket hub with heartbeat and agent events

- Wire WebSocket handlers.ts into main server (replacing agent-ws.ts)
- Add startHeartbeat() on server startup for connection health
- Add startAgentEvents() to bridge agent state machine to WebSocket hub
- Create agent-events.ts service for real-time agent event publishing
  - Publishes state.change on agent:state:{agentId}
  - Publishes output.chunk on agent:output:{agentId}
  - Publishes tool.start/tool.end on agent:tools:{agentId}

All 75 WebSocket tests passing.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>

